    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>第2次安装VIM，第1次学会了一些简单的命令，止步于不常用，这一次趁着要写博客，决定使用VIM来进行编辑工作。作为一个小菜鸟，不要求能飞多高，最重要的当下是 <strong>能飞</strong></p>
<a id="more"></a>
<h1 id="下载"><a href="#下载" class="headerlink" title="下载"></a>下载</h1><p>没什么好说的，度娘一下，这里贴上我下载的版本：<br><a href="&quot;ftp://ftp.vim.org/pub/vim/pc/gvim74-1024.exe&quot;">ftp://ftp.vim.org/pub/vim/pc/gvim74-1024.exe</a><br>下载成功后，一路next安装即可</p>
<h1 id="初识配置文件"><a href="#初识配置文件" class="headerlink" title="初识配置文件"></a>初识配置文件</h1><p>我的系统是windows，VIM安装在<code>C:\Program Files (x86)\Vim</code>路径下，<code>_vimrc</code>就是VIM的全局配置文件了。<br>打开后是下面这样子的：<br><figure class="highlight vim"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div><div class="line">27</div><div class="line">28</div><div class="line">29</div><div class="line">30</div><div class="line">31</div><div class="line">32</div><div class="line">33</div><div class="line">34</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="keyword">set</span> nocompatible</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">source</span> $VIMRUNTIME/vimrc_example.<span class="keyword">vim</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">source</span> $VIMRUNTIME/mswin.<span class="keyword">vim</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">behave</span> mswin</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">set</span> diffexpr=MyDiff()</div><div class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">MyDiff</span><span class="params">()</span></span></div><div class="line">  <span class="keyword">let</span> <span class="keyword">opt</span> = <span class="string">'-a --binary '</span></div><div class="line">  <span class="keyword">if</span> &amp;diffopt =~ <span class="string">'icase'</span> | <span class="keyword">let</span> <span class="keyword">opt</span> = <span class="keyword">opt</span> . <span class="string">'-i '</span> | <span class="keyword">endif</span></div><div class="line">  <span class="keyword">if</span> &amp;diffopt =~ <span class="string">'iwhite'</span> | <span class="keyword">let</span> <span class="keyword">opt</span> = <span class="keyword">opt</span> . <span class="string">'-b '</span> | <span class="keyword">endif</span></div><div class="line">  <span class="keyword">let</span> arg1 = <span class="variable">v:fname_in</span></div><div class="line">  <span class="keyword">if</span> arg1 =~ <span class="string">' '</span> | <span class="keyword">let</span> arg1 = <span class="string">'"'</span> . arg1 . <span class="string">'"'</span> | <span class="keyword">endif</span></div><div class="line">  <span class="keyword">let</span> arg2 = <span class="variable">v:fname_new</span></div><div class="line">  <span class="keyword">if</span> arg2 =~ <span class="string">' '</span> | <span class="keyword">let</span> arg2 = <span class="string">'"'</span> . arg2 . <span class="string">'"'</span> | <span class="keyword">endif</span></div><div class="line">  <span class="keyword">let</span> arg3 = <span class="variable">v:fname_out</span></div><div class="line">  <span class="keyword">if</span> arg3 =~ <span class="string">' '</span> | <span class="keyword">let</span> arg3 = <span class="string">'"'</span> . arg3 . <span class="string">'"'</span> | <span class="keyword">endif</span></div><div class="line">  <span class="keyword">if</span> $VIMRUNTIME =~ <span class="string">' '</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> &amp;<span class="keyword">sh</span> =~ <span class="string">'\&lt;cmd'</span></div><div class="line">      <span class="keyword">if</span> <span class="built_in">empty</span>(&amp;shellxquote)</div><div class="line">        <span class="keyword">let</span> <span class="variable">l:shxq_sav</span> = <span class="string">''</span></div><div class="line">        <span class="keyword">set</span> shellxquote&amp;</div><div class="line">      <span class="keyword">endif</span></div><div class="line">      <span class="keyword">let</span> cmd = <span class="string">'"'</span> . $VIMRUNTIME . <span class="string">'\diff"'</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span></div><div class="line">      <span class="keyword">let</span> cmd = <span class="keyword">substitute</span>($VIMRUNTIME, <span class="string">' '</span>, <span class="string">'" '</span>, <span class="string">''</span>) . <span class="string">'\diff"'</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">endif</span></div><div class="line">  <span class="keyword">else</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">let</span> cmd = $VIMRUNTIME . <span class="string">'\diff'</span></div><div class="line">  <span class="keyword">endif</span></div><div class="line">  <span class="keyword">silent</span> <span class="keyword">execute</span> <span class="string">'!'</span> . cmd . <span class="string">' '</span> . <span class="keyword">opt</span> . arg1 . <span class="string">' '</span> . arg2 . <span class="string">' &gt; '</span> . arg3</div><div class="line">  <span class="keyword">if</span> <span class="built_in">exists</span>(<span class="string">'l:shxq_sav'</span>)</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">let</span> &amp;shellxquote=<span class="variable">l:shxq_sav</span></div><div class="line">  <span class="keyword">endif</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">endfunction</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>本能告诉我，这是一段很NB的代码，鉴于目的是使用VIM来编辑博文，所以向下一步进行。</p>
<h1 id="插件包管理"><a href="#插件包管理" class="headerlink" title="插件包管理"></a>插件包管理</h1><p>由于是使用hexo搭建的博客，且默认新建文档都是Markdown格式的，所以就想着使用VIM扩展一个Markdown插件来进行编写，同时可以学习VIM/Markdown，挺划算的。在安装之前，凭借菜鸟的多年“菜鸟”经验，我应该先装一个管理插件的插件，随手一搜，发现了Vundle,二话不说，下载安装（按照官网提供的方式<code>git clone https://github.com/gmarik/vundle.git vim/vimfiles/bundle/vundle</code>,中间有个小插曲，windows开启了UAC控制，所以命令行要以管理员身份运行），一气呵成，附下地址 <a href="&quot;https://github.com/VundleVim/Vundle.vim&quot;">https://github.com/VundleVim/Vundle.vim</a></p>
<ul>
<li>修改配置文件<br>采用最小化改动原则，在原有配置文件基础之上，按照官方的配置进行增量添加，主要添加以下几行：<figure class="highlight vim"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="keyword">filetype</span> off		<span class="comment">" 必须</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">set</span> rtp+=$VIM/vimfiles/bundle/vundle <span class="comment">" 设置包括 vundle 和初始化相关的 runtime path</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">call</span> vundle#begin(<span class="string">'$VIM/vimfiles/bundle/'</span>) <span class="comment">" 指定一个 vundle 安装插件的路径</span></div><div class="line">Plugin <span class="string">'VundleVim/Vundle.vim'</span><span class="comment">" 让 vundle 管理插件版本 必须</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">call</span> vundle#end()            <span class="comment">" 必须</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">filetype</span> plugin <span class="built_in">indent</span> <span class="keyword">on</span>    <span class="comment">" 必须 加载vim自带和插件相应的语法和文件类型相关脚本</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<p>至此就配置好了，在VIM中输入<code>:PluginInstall</code>即可安装插件，噢，忘了说最重要的部分：<strong>所有的插件配置信息需要填写在<code>call vundle#begin</code>和<code>call vundle#end()</code>之间</strong></p>
<h1 id="VIM-Markdown"><a href="#VIM-Markdown" class="headerlink" title="VIM + Markdown"></a>VIM + Markdown</h1><p>在上述配置好后，终于可以要进入正题了，按照崇拜已久的大神<a href="http://stormzhang.com/" target="_blank" rel="external">stormzhang</a>的一篇文章<a href="http://stormzhang.com/github/2016/07/28/learn-github-from-zero7/" target="_blank" rel="external">如何发现优秀的开源项目？</a>,在github中输入<code>vim markdown</code>并按照<code>most star</code>进行排序，不用多说，就用第一个了！<br><img src="http://obzf18hto.bkt.clouddn.com/github-vim-markdown-star.png" alt=""></p>
<p>由于有了Vundle（感谢作者）这个利器，安装插件就容易多了，在配置文件中增加如下代码：<br><figure class="highlight vim"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">Plugin <span class="string">'godlygeek/tabular'</span>		<span class="comment">" 安装markdown必须先装tabular</span></div><div class="line">Plugin <span class="string">'plasticboy/vim-markdown'</span>	<span class="comment">" mardown 插件</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>打开VIM执行命令<code>:PluginInstall</code>,然后看网速，等待就好了，过程很快的。<br>安装完毕后，打开<code>.md</code>文件后就会有相应的语法高亮哦~<br><img src="http://obzf18hto.bkt.clouddn.com/markdown-syntax-example.png" alt=""></p>
<h1 id="Markdown-实时预览"><a href="#Markdown-实时预览" class="headerlink" title="Markdown 实时预览"></a>Markdown 实时预览</h1><p>成功运行后，其实自己的第一真实反应是</p>
<blockquote>
<p>我要原谅自己的无知，毕竟我是一只菜鸟~</p>
</blockquote>
<p>因为自己天真的以为安装完插件就可以做到实时预览博文了，下面是我预想的样子：<br><img src="http://obzf18hto.bkt.clouddn.com/markdown-multi-window.png" alt=""><br>既然没有达到理想的状态，就继续gihub</p>
<blockquote>
<p>VIM markdown preview</p>
</blockquote>
<p>这回没有选择<code>star</code>排名第一的（因为第一的不支持<code>WINDOWS</code>），这回选择了<br><a href="https://github.com/iamcco/markdown-preview.vim" target="_blank" rel="external">https://github.com/iamcco/markdown-preview.vim</a></p>
<ul>
<li>安装<br>依旧是在配置文件中添加代码（再一次感谢Vundle的作者）:<figure class="highlight vim"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">Plugin <span class="string">'iamcco/markdown-preview.vim'</span>	<span class="comment">"markdown 实时预览插件</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<p>执行命令 <code>:PluginInstall</code><br>安装完毕进行简单的配置如下：<br><figure class="highlight vim"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="keyword">let</span> <span class="variable">g:mkdp_path_to_chrome</span> = <span class="string">'C:/Program Files (x86)/Google/Chrome/Application/chrome.exe'</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">" 设置 chrome 浏览器的路径（或是启动 chrome（或其他现代浏览器）的命令）</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">let</span> <span class="variable">g:mkdp_auto_start</span> = <span class="number">0</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">" 设置为 1 可以在打开 markdown 文件的时候自动打开浏览器预览，只在打开</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">" markdown 文件的时候打开一次</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">let</span> <span class="variable">g:mkdp_auto_open</span> = <span class="number">0</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">" 设置为 1 在编辑 markdown 的时候检查预览窗口是否已经打开，否则自动打开预</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">" 览窗口</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">let</span> <span class="variable">g:mkdp_auto_close</span> = <span class="number">1</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">" 在切换 buffer 的时候自动关闭预览窗口，设置为 0 则在切换 buffer 的时候不</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">" 自动关闭预览窗口</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">let</span> <span class="variable">g:mkdp_refresh_slow</span> = <span class="number">0</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">" 设置为 1 则只有在保存文件，或退出插入模式的时候更新预览，默认为 0，实时</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">" 更新预览</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>在VIM中输入命令 <code>:MarkdownPreview</code> 即可，支持实时预览哦~<br>好了，终于实现我想要的了，贴张图：<br><img src="http://obzf18hto.bkt.clouddn.com/markdow-realtime-preview-ok.png" alt=""></p>
]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;第2次安装VIM，第1次学会了一些简单的命令，止步于不常用，这一次趁着要写博客，决定使用VIM来进行编辑工作。作为一个小菜鸟，不要求能飞多高，最重要的当下是 &lt;strong&gt;能飞&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
